                    </div>
                    <span>I was surprized by the quality of the works presented but more particularly the idea of "the architecture of adventure". The premise of this book is "right on." These get-aways are not just comfortable, but expose their owner's attitudes on being at home in nature.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great looking with great ideas...</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
